<Content>Very Good chioce!!! Been there 3 night's with my wife and baby boy (1.2 year old), got the junior suite upgrading free of charge. and i got to choose regular bed or water bed, took the second one again free of charge. the location is far from the center of berlin but not so far with urban train that locate 5 steps from the hotel, only 15 min away. easy to use and with a baby too. There 3 min walk to a great shopping mall and a cheap supermarket in the hotel building.Next time in berlin we will be there again. 
